These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, reading, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, sports, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, tennis, weightlifting, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, car, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
 2. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
 3. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8
 5. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 8. the person watching spy movies is between the person driving the car and the person who's sport is tennis##2
 9. the person driving the van is the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
13. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the train##1
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who's sport is tennis##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | chess     | rock-climbing   | magic-tricks | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | spy   | adventure   | sports  |
| Sport         | tennis  | weightlifting  | handball  | badminton |
| Transport     | scooter    | train | car     | van    |

