.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, coffee, fanta
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, lettuce, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, soul, r&b, punk
4 different pets are kept: mouse, fish, cat, hamster
 1. the fan of r&b is between the owner of the mouse and the fan of soul##2
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
 5. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the fan of soul##8
 6. the person eating raspberry is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 8. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of hip-hop is the owner of the fish##1
10. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
11. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
12. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
14. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
15. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
17. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan of soul##8
18. the person eating pineapple is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
19. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee | fanta  | soy-milk  |
| Food          | raspberry     | pineapple | cauliflower | lettuce  |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | r&b  | punk | hip-hop |
| Pet           | cat | hamster | mouse    | fish  |

