.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess, gardening, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, adventure, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, disco, ambient, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, golf, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the fan of indie##5
 5. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person watching documentary movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8
 7. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
11. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
12. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing    | collecting   | gardening | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | adventure  | crime   | musical      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | indie    | ambient      | d&b       |
| Sport         | golf    | rowing | baseball   | skateboarding    |

