 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person eating mango##8
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the lawyer##1
10. the bartender is the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person eating papaya##8
12. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
14. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
15. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4

