 6. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the russian##8
 7. the person drinking 7up is not the indonesian##6
 8. the videographer is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person drinking 7up##7
 9. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
10. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the videographer##3
11. the electrician is on the right of the chef##1
12. the videographer is not the canadian##6
13. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
14. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
