.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, tea, milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, r&b, electronic, house
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, soccer, skiing, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, tram, roller
 1. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 8. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the fan of r&b##8
11. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate   | milk     | tea    | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | house      | electronic     | r&b     |
| Sport         | surfing | skiing  | sailing     | soccer  |
| Transport     | helicopter     | tram | roller | taxi     |

