 3. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the analyst is the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is not the photographer##6
 6. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
 7. the person watching satire movies is not to the left of the photographer##8
 8. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 9. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
11. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is chess is between the photographer and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
13. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
